{"type": "article", "id": 32144, "title": "象牙或将不再被用于首饰，以及，贝嫂 2017 春夏系列主推睡衣风 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-13T02:33:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2944, "name": "伦敦时装周"}, {"id": 32703, "name": "WCC"}, {"id": 32704, "name": "瑞士腕表"}, {"id": 2882, "name": "Tory Burch"}, {"id": 7422, "name": "Nasty Gal"}, {"id": 8195, "name": "Banana Republic"}, {"id": 26358, "name": "A Bathing Ape"}, {"id": 32705, "name": "CARAHRTT WIP"}, {"id": 2836, "name": "Victoria Beckham"}, {"id": 21038, "name": "Olivia Palermo"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160913095527bUgzECBOenxK1ZYj.png", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/marketing-promotion/bfc-british-fashion-council-caroline-rush-new-internal-team-10539451/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>英国时尚协会任命了三个新的主管</b></a> | 在伦敦时装周 9 月 20 日正式开幕之前，作为主办方，英国时尚协会任命了三个新的主管。其中，Clara Mercer 为公关主管，Jenico Preston 为商务主管，Laura Strain 则是财政主管。这三个新的主管将直接向英国时尚协会的首席执行官 Caroline Rush 汇报工作。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/nasty-gal-seeking-buyer-sophia-amoruso-revolve-10541444/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国女性服饰电商 Nasty Gal 寻求买家</b></a> | 有消息称，Nasty Gal 正在积极地寻求买家。此前，Nasty Gal 分别于 2012 年获得来自 Index Ventures 的 4900 万美元投资，以及 2015 年来自 Apple 零售之父 Ron Johnson 的 1600 万美元的投资。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/government-trade/new-support-ban-ivory-use-10539717/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>世界自然保护大会要求各国停止象牙交易</b></a> | 此项决议于上个周六在夏威夷火奴鲁鲁举办的世界自然保护大会 (WCC) 上通过，它要求各国政府采取法律措施，关闭象牙交易市场。象牙或将不再被用于珠宝首饰中。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/designer-luxury/tory-burch-taps-john-douglas-as-chief-technology-officer-10539671/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Tory Burch 集团任命新的 CTO</b></a> | John Douglas 被任命为 Tory Burch 的新 CTO 。他曾经担任 MCM 时尚集团的信息总监，以及 Burberry 的技术总监。据 Tory Burch 的首席执行官称，John Douglas 丰富的经验将帮助集团更好地进行数字创新。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>诞生于美国的人气工装品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/carhartt-wip-2016-fall-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">CARAHRTT WIP 2016 秋冬系列</a>即将全面上架。该系列有「CARAHRTT ATHLETICS」、「CART RACING」、「MILITARY」 这三个主题，以贴身剪裁及上乘布料来展现品牌的高品质。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094452BmhStuMDQZ10bAR5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094452ZuQ8kyoDgmfFpGwr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094452MO6FWgrCveaYtj12.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094452A3UzwyRpCOuh8PTD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094452ziMuGJLVdRhXCDmg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094453qo4wA6Xa2JSpUdvf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094453dci0benEJ5jHI7Cr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094452zixQIdYHjmnDr3Kb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094453hS9RHUcLZNmDYvdi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/victoria-beckham-spring-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Victoria Beckham 发布 2017 春夏系列</a>，以丝绸和天鹅绒为主要素材，主推休闲睡衣风。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094505n84krsVFaKqPgTOx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094504tpnKE9OcsDbaSLyG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094504Hlj7dRCG3P9XUWIh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094505PVXFcLS2Mi35Jarw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094505jrzXfpZi30d2lcax.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094505hZHMB5i67gCYUaKL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">推荐一个瑞士的腕表品牌 MYKU。它的首个腕表系列名为 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/myku-unique-watch-at-woaw-store\" rel=\"nofollow\">「Elemental Classic Series I」</a>。主推简洁、经典的风格。表盘选用了天然大理石切割而成，每一块表盘的纹理都有所区别，它还使用了意大利真皮表带，使佩戴更为舒适。该系列手表价格在 5000 人民币左右。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094647qpvG5X0boiIVw2Lm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094647YHKG2xNbAicl5mfJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094647WQKATuegn2pm4FyJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094647lDXTYkqgHbadABhf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094647X5syCpvjZq6JVLdK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094648pUflFchPoWKkby5S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/olivia-palermo-banana-republic-2016-looks/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Olivia Palermo 成为 Banana Republic 新的形象代言人</a>。她在纽约为 Banana Republic 拍摄了一组新的宣传大片，由 Jason Kim 掌镜。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094656ZSbFEJCNrIVWixMB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094656OYieKDpS2ruLVUFZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609130946561fceoSrTtapdB4Q9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094656RnWOp3HS4PQjNBKT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094656gkyLdt4JXcMoARb8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609130946565oOXCM0zVsqRfA26.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/bape-street-fighter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">A Bathing Ape 推出《街头霸王》联名新品</a>。该系列包括了布兰卡、春丽、肯、桑吉尔夫、本田等经典角色，将于 9 月 17 日登陆品牌门店及线上商店。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">&nbsp;<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094706VCY5GKTuRweQnsh2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094706nKwMXiJx6yp3oSq0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094706Kdt1NzDQSE2PgULH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094706fW0xX5SeloF4mvYn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094706OEFjKvADx7SY0ZXr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094707CB6sEUxlewjnSHcv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094707CVZirMIzs47Fe3Wd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016091309470707nEkLTaye9Yzhit.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160913094707d6VqxyUaXeQifW2B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}